utor 在 mv→validation/package/ 后 combined quality 曾因 studio 旧 dist 类型失败，但同次 run 已打印 quality:engine ok，随后 build+quality:studio 绿。官方 VERIFY_BATCH 仍须跑任务 verify（quality:engine）。ENGINE-STRUCT-009 对 validation/package 等为既有告警非硬失败。\"\n}\n","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":37,"fileSize":2153,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/.ai-workflow-v2-engine-io-ports/reviews/latest.json","readRange":{"startLine":1,"endLine":37},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-2306e65e-e311-480d-ad04-dc41a9d96d78-31\nfc_83d0c451-e609-952f-bff4-00fd396cbccb_0","startedAtMs":"1784784763089","completedAtMs":"1784784763244"},"model_call_id":"51f4eeec-4abc-4338-82b6-7ffa26490294-7-78ns","session_id":"a3680f7e-0b6d-44a0-bebb-f72e7a9829f8","timestamp_ms":1784784763199}
